      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "[59] Bĕsêpher, “in a book,” and bassêpher. “in the book, differ only in the pointing, which, resting solely on tradition cannot be entirely depended on. The LXX. omit the article.",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
