            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "Joshua 1:7",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": " that so it might be kept in memory, and transmitted to the latest posterity; it being on the one hand an instance of great impiety, inhumanity, and rashness, in Amalek, and on the other a display of the goodness, kindness, and power of God on the behalf of his people: and ",
            "children": []
