        "text": " - ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "Write this...  in a book",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The original has, \"Write this in the book.\" It is clear that a book already existed, in which Moses entered events of interest, and that now he was divinely commanded to record in it the great victory over Amalek, and the threat uttered against them. The record was to be for a memorial - ",
        "children": []
      },
