        "class": "Text_Heading",
        "text": "2.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " that when the fulfilment of the threat came (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "1 Chronicles 4:43",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), God might have his due honour, and his name be glorified. ",
        "children": []
