        "text": "i.e.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", to thy successor, Joshua, the tradition of perpetual hostility with Amalek, and the memory of the promise now made, that the whole nation shall be utterly blotted out from under heaven. (Compare ",
        "children": []
